      <S N="Description">Carbon is a PowerShell module for automating the configuration Windows 7, 8, 2008, and 2012 and automation the installation and configuration of Windows applications, websites, and services. It can configure and manage:_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_ * Local users and groups_x000D__x000A_ * IIS websites, virtual directories, and applications_x000D__x000A_ * File system, registry, and certificate permissions_x000D__x000A_ * Certificates_x000D__x000A_ * Privileges_x000D__x000A_ * Services_x000D__x000A_ * Encryption_x000D__x000A_ * Junctions_x000D__x000A_ * Hosts file_x000D__x000A_ * INI files_x000D__x000A_ * Performance counters_x000D__x000A_ * Shares_x000D__x000A_ * .NET connection strings and app settings_x000D__x000A_ * And much more!_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_All functions are idempotent: when run multiple times with the same arguments, your system will be in the same state without failing or producing errors.</S>
